A vintage-style technical illustration depicting a complex mechanical mail sorting machine with pneumatic tubes, brass gears, and analog dials, seamlessly integrated with glowing fiber optic cables and circuit board patterns. The machine sits in a warmly lit workshop environment with wooden workbenches, old technical blueprints pinned to walls, and amber-toned lighting casting dramatic shadows. Steam wisps rise from copper pipes while data streams flow through transparent tubes like luminescent liquid. The aesthetic blends Victorian-era industrial machinery with early computing elements, creating a steampunk-adjacent vision of server infrastructure.
